(2697, 1001, 2688, 2688, 576, 'Error while importing into mysql.', 'could you replace MySQLName by this code and make another try; I had no time to test this, but hopefully it will work\r\n\r\n\' to translate MSSQL names to legal MySQL names\r\n\' replace blank, -, ( and ) by \'_\'\r\nFunction MySQLName(tmp)\r\n  tmp = Replace(tmp, \" \", \"_\")\r\n  tmp = Replace(tmp, \"-\", \"_\")\r\n  tmp = Replace(tmp, \"(\", \"_\")\r\n  \' the next line has changed\r\n  MySQLName = \"\'\" & Replace(tmp, \")\", \"_\") & \"\'\"\r\nEnd Function\r\n\r\nfeedback is welcome!', '2003-10-30 11:19:28'),
