(3362, 1001, 3351, 3351, 576, 'Export into existing table', 'If the database and all tables already exist, you could try to change the procedure ConvertDatabase like this:\r\n\r\nPrivate Sub ConvertDatabase()\r\n  \' copy database schema\r\n  Dim dmoDB \'As SQLDMO.Database\r\n  Set dmoDB = dmoSrv.Databases(MSSQL_DB_NAME)\r\n  \' DBDefinition dmoDB   \'<------ comment character \' added\r\n  \' copy data\r\n  CopyDB dmoDB\r\nEnd Sub\r\n\r\nI am sorry, but I have no time to test this or to add another option to mssql2mysql right now.', '2004-06-21 13:48:33'),
